EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: A measurement of the H1 specific IgG antibody secreting cells in a biological specimen.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: A measurement of the H3 specific IgG antibody secreting cells in a biological specimen.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: A measurement of the total IgG antibody secreting cells in a biological specimen.
